{"tid":1854162,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新加坡即日起停發簽證給中國旅客 並撤銷之前簽證","createTime":"2020-01-31T10:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T13:23:07.000Z","uid":144372,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f7ec465cdfc4d6cb0618e2999d14ce90b51f51","tid":1854162,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4314346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F4314346&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=db6b9455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4314346</a><br />\n<br />\n隨著武漢肺炎疫情在中國湖北以外的省市擴展，新加坡政府決定從後天（2月2日）起，禁止所有過去14天曾到中國大陸的旅客入境新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n然而，從中國大陸入境的新加坡公民、永久居民和長期執照持有者，仍能回返新加坡，但當局要求他們申請14天的缺席假。<br />\n<br />\n政府也將從即日起，暫停簽發各種准證給中國的訪客，之前簽發的短期簽證和多次入境簽證也會被撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織昨天（30日）宣布把中國武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒肺炎）疫情定為國際關注的突發公共衛生事件。截至昨日下午2時，本地確診病例總數達13起，全部都是來自武漢的中國公民。"},{"pid":"c1787a3eea1ec2b055cd232c129d4a35ecaa5245","tid":1854162,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b1898f3b71ec41c1ded7bbc05ea71d179dad6c4","tid":1854162,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武肺背後嘅第三次世界大戰：諜戰丶生化戰丶經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854117</a><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d64efe0207866d80ca0cf1b53a1264fdcfde09c2","tid":1854162,"uid":59870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"香港都禁？"},{"pid":"82045b3ebdd2f6799f351be1860480196936dbb2","tid":1854162,"uid":110579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"坡仔終於做到香港人想香港政府做到嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738a7e66e7c5205c5cd2ea6f34e57f41ba7f533c","tid"